OL,3,CColourful charity run raises vital
OL,4,Cfunds for Hospice
OL,6,F1,600 people were sprayed with colour
OL,7,Fon the charity run for Trinity Hospice
OL,8,Fin Blackpool
OL,10,FCharity runners in Blackpool have been
OL,11,Fsprayed with colour, all to raise
OL,12,Fabout #50,000 for Trinity Hospice.
OL,14,FMore than 1,600 people took to the
OL,15,Fbeach to take part in the annual
OL,16,FBlackpool Colour Run.
OL,18,FThe event that helps fund vital
OL,19,Fhospice care saw young and old join
OL,20,Ftogether to run through theJcolourful
OL,21,Fcourse at Starr Gate Beach.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
