OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784549891
OL,3,CColourful charity run raises vital
OL,4,Cfunds for Hospice
OL,6,FThe crowds passed through seven powder
OL,7,Fpaint stations before crossing the
OL,8,Ffinish line covered in every colour of
OL,9,Fthe rainbow.JTrinity's Events
OL,10,FFundraiser, Danny Hickes, said:
OL,12,F"What an incredible day. To see more
OL,13,Fthan 1,600 people join together to
OL,14,Fsupport local hospice care was
OL,15,Fgenuinely inspiring. Every splash of
OL,16,Fcolour represented someone choosing to
OL,17,Fmake a difference for local families
OL,18,Ffacing
OL,20,Fsome of life's most difficult moments."
OL,26,@tD@AOU
